```plantuml
@startuml(adityajain10_foot365-live-streaming-chatbot-prediction-app-on-aws)

actor User

box "Frontend" #LightBlue
    participant "JavaScript" as JS
    participant "HTML/CSS" as HTML
end box

box "AWS Cloud" #LightYellow
    box "API Gateway" #LightGreen
        participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
    end box

    box "Lambda Functions" #LightCoral
        participant "standings.py" as Standings
        participant "predictions.py" as Predictions
        participant "LF2.py" as LF2
        participant "getFixtures.py" as GetFixtures
        participant "scrapeMatchData.py" as ScrapeData
        participant "getScore.py" as GetScore
        participant "LF1.py" as LF1
        participant "getLiveScores.py" as GetLiveScores
    end box

    box "AWS Services" #LightPink
        participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
        participant "ElasticSearch" as ElasticSearch
        participant "SQS" as SQS
        participant "SNS" as SNS
        participant "S3" as S3
    end box
end box

User -> JS: Access Frontend
JS -> APIGateway: Request Match Data
APIGateway -> Standings: Fetch Standings (DynamoDB)
Standings -> DynamoDB: Query Standings
Standings -> APIGateway: Return Standings Data
APIGateway -> JS: Forward Standings Data

JS -> APIGateway: Request Predictions
APIGateway -> Predictions: Invoke Prediction Logic (SageMaker)
Predictions -> DynamoDB: Store Predictions
Predictions -> APIGateway: Return Prediction Data
APIGateway -> JS: Forward Prediction Data

User -> JS: Chat with Chatbot
JS -> APIGateway: Invoke Chatbot (Lex)
APIGateway -> LF1: Process Chatbot Request
LF1 -> ElasticSearch: Query Fixtures
LF1 -> DynamoDB: Query Match Results
LF1 -> SNS: Send SMS Notification
LF1 -> APIGateway: Return Chatbot Response
APIGateway -> JS: Forward Chatbot Response

S3 -> ScrapeData: Event Trigger
ScrapeData -> DynamoDB: Store Parsed Match Data

APIGateway -> GetLiveScores: Request Live Scores
GetLiveScores -> DynamoDB: Query Live Scores
GetLiveScores -> APIGateway: Return Live Scores
APIGateway -> JS: Forward Live Scores

@enduml
```